submittedAt.description: The timestamp when the form was submitted.

updatedAt.description: The timestamp when the form submission data was last updated.

values.description: An array of form field values submitted in the form.

name.description: The name or identifier of the form field.

value.description: The actual value submitted for the form field.

objectTypeId.description: The type identifier of the form field value.

pageUrl.description: The URL of the web page where the form was submitted.

formId.description: The unique identifier of the form associated with the submission.
